>"},{"pid":"b5812484ee83c7e14ad751563d01d2e4a8e53eae","tid":2338123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"facb115417e28e163fc3ed22548f260e84177016","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7d87fc9e385cfe9ff34a540dd45c689cbe68c2","tid":2338123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dad0cf2927db37602b1e6f9312066936d5077fbb","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T21:51:25.000Z","msg":"「我殺了人，只因為夏日陽光刺眼太熱」<br />\n--莫梭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿拉伯人拎住把刀揚黎揚去只係切生果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:35:02.000Z","msg":"我唔介意阿拉伯人將個FD當切生果咁切<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信神，冇人救到你<br />\n信神就環保啲救埋啲海龜"},{"pid":"c101d7cf67faa106d10ffa6c0cd30ed956226cf6","tid":2338123,"uid":85260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbbaa4f73db3d3863d4773a44276075c84ce5d2c","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cff06e9fea5b97bdbc770888ce79eec2d7fd314c","tid":2338123,"uid":85260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ca5dd00334a32d6c7c059c2d600b448cb2cffce","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:07:12.000Z","msg":"「有個人早年離開自己的村子，外出謀生。過了二十五年，他發了財，帶著妻兒回家鄉。他母親與他妹妹在村里開了家旅店。為了要讓她們得到意外的驚喜，他把自己的妻子和兒子留在另一個地方，自己則住進他母親的旅館。<br />\n<br />\n進去時，他母親沒有認出他。他想開個大玩笑，就特意租了一個房間，並亮出自己的錢財。夜裡，他的母親與妹妹為了謀財，用大錘砸死了他，把屍體扔進了河裡。第二天早晨，他的妻子來了，懵然不知真情，通報了這位店客的姓名。<br />\n<br />\n最後母親上吊自盡，妹妹投井而死。<br />\n<br />\n這則報導，我天天反复閱讀，足足讀了幾千遍。<br />\n<br />\n一方面，這樁事不像是真的，另一方面，卻又自然而然。不論怎樣，我覺得這個店客有點咎由自取，人生在世，永遠也不該演戲作假。就這樣，我睡大覺、進行回憶、讀那則新聞報導，晝夜輪迴，日復一日，時間也就過去了。我過去在書裡讀到過，說人在監獄裡久而久之，最後就會失去時間觀念。<br />\n<br />\n但是，這對於我來說，並沒有多大意義。<br />\n<br />\n我一直不理解，在何種程度上，即可說日子慢慢難捱，又可說苦短無多。日子，過起來當然就長，但是拖拖拉拉，日復一日，年復一年，最後就混淆成了一片。<br />\n<br />\n每個日子都喪失了自己的名字。對我來說，只有&ldquo;昨天&rdquo;與&ldquo;明天&rdquo;這樣的字，才具有一定的意義。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:35:59.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇呢段<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:38:29.000Z","msg":"最鍾意呢段，最能突出荒謬的人世，卡繆睇黎都幾鐘意呢個故事，係之後的劇作都用左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:44:42.000Z","msg":"前排睇完到而家都釋懷什至理解唔到 擁抱荒謬呢個core value"},{"pid":"2d43bb3d982e85f9170fe992c9721a5a124c8e58","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5812484ee83c7e14ad751563d01d2e4a8e53eae","tid":2338123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"facb115417e28e163fc3ed22548f260e84177016","tid":2338123,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7d87fc9e385cfe9ff34a540dd45c689cbe68c2","tid":2338123,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿拉伯人拎住把刀揚黎揚去只係切生果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:35:02.000Z","msg":"我唔介意阿拉伯人將個FD當切生果咁切<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信神，冇人救到你<br />\n信神就環保啲救埋啲海龜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:45:37.000Z","msg":"神無權審判或拯救我的靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada1d6bed94777755c8125