faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T22:38:29.000Z","msg":"最鍾意呢段，最能突出荒謬的人世，卡繆睇黎都幾鐘意呢個故事，係之後的劇作都用左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"香港有話劇團做過，真心幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec7b2271b1a39b9cc78287b85d911732cefc90d","tid":2338123,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"想問下睇中文版同英文版分別大唔大"},{"pid":"c219fd9abf37dda758ae69ea61beed8b68c115ff","tid":2338123,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RDpWkBi-cr4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRDpWkBi-cr4&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=f78383e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RDpWkBi-cr4</a>"},{"pid":"81bb20a49f928fde7c3ef946ee028d6f322e1c88","tid":2338123,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"最後嗰章真係好令人感到好絕望"},{"pid":"4a50d310b86e44ca185da2724683e090963021c6","tid":2338123,"uid":180538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"你令我唸番起自己細個睇「哲學」<br />\n講真 真係純粹想自己特別d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家再睇番<br />\n感覺連「哲學」的意思都有d唔同左<br />\n先知道前人真係走到好遠好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528a0a33a3d666c238e623962ecc18d86db22de8","tid":2338123,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IfVI9hbw0eU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIfVI9hbw0eU&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=a6283278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/If